<subSubSection id="9983A9D91B08FFC4F84EFE27F750FD33" pageId="22" pageNumber="533" type="description">
<paragraph id="D126FA521B08FFC4F84EFE27F750FD33" blockId="22.[2008,2602,282,710]" lastBlockId="22.[1397,2605,718,1147]" pageId="22" pageNumber="533">
<emphasis id="E3ED26401B08FFC4F84EFE27F762FDAB" bold="true" box="[2010,2290,598,631]" pageId="22" pageNumber="533">Descriptive notes.</emphasis>
Head-body 160-177 mm (males) and 159-166 mm (females). No specific data are available for body weight. Rosendo Pascual’s Tuco-tuco is relatively small.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
